.planning/phases/12-server-side-outcomes-pre-aggregation/12-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:127:**Notes:** This is the central reuse of Phase 11 (as ROADMAP dependency note states). Add `/api/outcomes/aggregate` to `SKIP_AUDIT_PATHS`, handler calls `logAuditEntry({ name: "outcomes.aggregate", cohortHash: hashCohortId(cohortId), user, centers, payloadBytes, cacheHit })`.
