.planning/phases/12-server-side-outcomes-pre-aggregation/12-01-PLAN.md:97:Extract pure math + pure FHIR constants + FHIR domain types from `src/` into a top-level `shared/` directory, update both tsconfigs to include it, and install backward-compatibility re-export shims so every existing client-side import keeps working. This is the single precondition that unlocks Plan 12-02's server handler — without the split, a server import of `computeCohortTrajectory` transitively loads `authHeaders.ts` and crashes on `sessionStorage is not defined` (RESEARCH.md §Common Pitfalls #5, §Pattern 1).
