.planning/phases/11-audit-beacon-pii-hardening/11-RESEARCH.md:306:**How to avoid:** Migrate the assertion to: method === 'POST', `init.keepalive === true`, `JSON.parse(init.body)` contains `cohortId: 'abc'` (client still sends raw id; server hashes), `init.headers['Content-Type']` === `application/json`.
.planning/phases/11-audit-beacon-pii-hardening/11-RESEARCH.md:309:### Pitfall 5: Startup ordering — `initHashCohortId` must run before any request could reach the handler
