.planning/phases/11-audit-beacon-pii-hardening/11-RESEARCH.md:318:**How to avoid:** Either (a) add `audit.cohortHashSecret` required-check to `validateSettingsSchema`, or (b) keep the startup-only model and document that rotating the secret requires a restart. Decision belongs to the planner; option (b) is simpler and aligns with the JWT-secret model (`initAuth.ts` never re-reads the secret from settings).
