.planning/phases/11-audit-beacon-pii-hardening/11-02-SUMMARY.md:203:With Plan 11-02 merged the server rejects the legacy GET with 404 — so **Plan 11-03 must ship before any client that relies on the GET transport**, or view-open events are silently lost. This sequencing matches the phase wave plan.
