.planning/phases/16-cross-cohort-comparison/16-REVIEW.md:164:**Issue:** The OTP value `123456` is a static code used in tests (`cohortCompareDrawer.test.tsx` and routing tests reference OTP as a stub). If the demo OTP is ever a real rotating TOTP, having it hardcoded in tests and i18n simultaneously creates a maintenance coupling. Already covered by CR-01 for the security dimension; flagged here as a test-maintenance concern. No separate fix required beyond CR-01.
