.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:7:**Phase:** 15-totp-2fa
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:23:**Notes:** User previously declined to generate a UI-SPEC for this phase, confirming minimal frontend changes are expected. All decisions in CONTEXT.md represent Claude's judgment for a production clinical security application, following Phase 14 PasswordChangePage patterns where applicable.
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:29:- Enrollment UI (D-02): TotpEnrollPage full-page interstitial, same pattern as PasswordChangePage
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:31:- Admin reset (D-04): "Reset 2FA" button in AdminPage user row, DELETE /api/auth/users/:username/totp
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-DISCUSSION-LOG.md:33:- Library choice (D-09): otplib@13.4.0 + qrcode@1.5.4
