.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:519:| T-15-08 | Elevation of Privilege | POST /verify recovery code brute force | mitigate | Same rate limiter; each code 32-bit entropy (`crypto.randomBytes(4)`); 10 codes per user = 10 × 2^32 search space |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:520:| T-15-09 | Information Disclosure | enrollToken payload includes totpSecret | mitigate | JWT signed HS256 with server secret; client cannot decode without key; 3-min TTL limits window; add to REDACT_FIELDS (Plan 01 Task 4) |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:521:| T-15-10 | Replay | Burned recovery code reuse | mitigate | modifyUsers() removes matched hash atomically under write lock BEFORE response; second attempt finds no match in array |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:523:| T-15-12 | Spoofing | Non-admin triggers DELETE /users/:username/totp | mitigate | Task 3: handler rejects `req.auth.role !== 'admin'` with 403 before touching users.json |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:524:| T-15-13 | Elevation of Privilege | enrollToken reused as session Bearer | mitigate | Plan 01 Task 3 adds `totp-enroll` to verifyLocalToken purpose-rejection list; cannot authenticate protected routes |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:525:| T-15-14 | Denial of Service | /totp/confirm spammed to exhaust bcrypt | accept | bcrypt cost ~300ms × 10 codes concurrent = ~350ms per confirm; rate limiter gates /login which issues enrollToken; impact bounded |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:526:| T-15-15 | Information Disclosure | Recovery codes logged in audit DB | mitigate | Plan 01 Task 4 redacts response bodies on /totp/confirm; audit writes REDACTED placeholder |
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-02-PLAN.md:527:| T-15-16 | Elevation of Privilege | TOCTOU on recovery code burn | mitigate | Task 2: burn happens inside `modifyUsers()` callback under the serialized write lock; concurrent /verify calls see post-burn state |
