.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-CONTEXT.md:74:- `.planning/REQUIREMENTS.md` — SEC-04 (TOTP RFC 6238 enrollment), SEC-05 (recovery codes bcrypt-hashed, burned on use)
.planning/phases/15-totp-2fa/15-CONTEXT.md:77:- `tests/mustChangePassword.test.ts` — Template for backend TOTP tests (same setup pattern: create temp dir, initAuth, mock users)
