   100	#### Phase 17: Audit Log Upgrade & Dark Mode
   101	**Goal**: Administrators can filter and search the audit log by multiple dimensions; all users can switch between light, dark, and system color themes with WCAG-compliant chart colors in both modes
   102	**Depends on**: Phase 14
